{"name":"Vespera Argent","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"","alignment":"unaligned","hitDice":"37","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":6,"otherArmorDesc":"12 (natural armor)","speed":"40","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"40","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"351 (37d8 + 185)","speedDesc":"40 ft.","strPoints":"20","dexPoints":"18","conPoints":"20","intPoints":"24","wisPoints":"22","chaPoints":"24","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"50","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"30","telepathy":0,"cr":"19","customCr":"2 (450 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":true,"legendariesDescription":"Vespera can use any of the following abilities once per encounter after another player's turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the giant boar can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the giant boar can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The giant boar can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the giant boar's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the giant boar's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the giant boar dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Silver Spears","desc":"Vespera makes three attacks with her silver spears, each one can be any of the spear actions below. Creatures hit by the spear attack auto-fail any associated saving throws if there is an AOE. She can either do that or cast a spell."},{"name":"Legendary Resistance (3/day)","desc":"If [MON] fails a saving throw, it can succeed instead. This imposes disadvantage on his spell attacks for the next turn."}],"actions":[{"name":"Silver Rush","desc":"_Ranged Spell Attack:_ [CHA ATK] to hit, range 60/120 ft., multiple targets in a line. _Hit:_ [CHA 3D8] piercing damage, [3D8] lightning damage."},{"name":"Pierce the Veil","desc":"_Ranged Spell Attack:_ [CHA ATK] to hit, range 60/120 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [CHA 3D8] piercing damage. A cloud of magical smoke and darkness emanates from the spear in a 20 ft. radius, lasting one turn."},{"name":"Incendiary Spear","desc":"_Ranged Spell Attack:_ [CHA ATK] to hit, range 60/120 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [CHA 3D8] piercing damage, [3D8] fire damage. Target is set ablaze. They can spend their bonus action patting the flames down or take an extra [3D8] fire damage."},{"name":"Chill Out","desc":"_Ranged Spell Attack:_ [CHA ATK] to hit, range 60/120 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [CHA 3D8] piercing damage, [3D8] cold damage. Target's speed is reduced by half."},{"name":"Fireball","desc":"(At will) Range 150 ft., Each creature in a 20-foot-radius sphere centered on that point must make a Dexterity [CHA SAVE] saving throw. A target takes 8d6 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one."},{"name":"Lightning Bolt","desc":"(At will) Range 100 ft line: A stroke of lightning forming a 100-foot-long, 5-foot-wide Line blasts out from you in a direction you choose. Each creature in the Line makes a Dexterity [CHA SAVE] saving throw, taking [8D6] Lightning damage on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one."},{"name":"Delayed Blast Fireball","desc":"2/DAY - CONCENTRATION - 1 MINUTE - 150ft RANGE - When the spell ends, the bead explodes and each creature in a 20-foot-radius sphere centered on that point makes a DC [CHA SAVE] DEX save. Take 12d6 + 1d6 for each turn it doesn't detonate and half that on a save. If a creature touches it before the spell ends, they make a DC [CHA SAVE] DEX saving throw, on a fail it explodes. On a save they can throw it up to 40 ft."},{"name":"Disintegrate","desc":"2/Day, range 60 ft. A creature targeted by this spell must make a DC [CHA SAVE] Dexterity saving throw. On a failed save, the target takes 10d6 + 40 force damage. If this damage reduces the target to 0 hit points, it is disintegrated. A disintegrated creature and everything it is wearing and carrying, except magic items, are reduced to a pile of fine gray dust."},{"name":"Power Word Kill","desc":"1/ Day, range 60 FT You compel one creature you can see within range to die. If the creature you choose has 100 hit points or fewer, it dies."},{"name":"Time Stop","desc":"1/DAY - Time stops for everyone but herself. You take 1d4 + 1 turns during which you can use your actions and move as normal. Ends when you affect anyone but yourself."},{"name":"Teleport","desc":"2 / Day. Teleport."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Telekinetic Yank","desc":"30 ft. range, you target a creature you can see of size medium or smaller, they make a strength saving throw DC [CHA SAVE] or are pulled 20 feet in the direction of Vespera's choosing. A creature cannot fall as a result of this spell, if they encounter a ledge they stop before falling."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Force Field","desc":"Vespera erects a force field in between any silver spears that are on the ground. Nothing physical can pass through it, it acts like the wall of force spell. It is 30 ft. tall. The attacker may chose a new target."},{"name":"Electric Gate","desc":"Vespera shocks anything in between her spears, the target must make a DC [CHA SAVE] CHA saving throw, or take [CHA 4D8] lightning damage and be jolted. Jolted targets must chose in between 2/3 actions of action, bonus action, or movement."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"int","order":3},{"name":"wis","order":4},{"name":"cha","order":5}],"skills":[],"damagetypes":[{"name":"poison","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"psychic","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"blinded"},{"name":"charmed"},{"name":"frightened"},{"name":"paralyzed"},{"name":"poisoned"}],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":7,"damage":[]}